  • Welcome to Hextml at 2019-12-28T15:55:15.533Z (3.12MB)
Here you can upload resources (one by one or multiples at the same time).
  • An image resource can be an image that you will be able to use as terrain or as a background for the map (try the "opacity" feature). The text field is for the background color
  • A text resource is a map that can be imported.

Read my campaign notes with pictures and maps :)

Hextml is an online hex map maker, world building tool, campaign manager and virtual tabletop software for your RPG. Use it in your DnD (or any other tabletop RPG) campaign to build a world for you and your players. It uses the best of HTML5 to let you make beautiful hexagonal maps. You can share a map live with your players by enabling the collaborative mode (with or without fog of war).

Ask quetions about the software here, I visit this post quite often.

Hextml is made by made by playest
